    Represents a scientific or research experiment containing a name and a collection of Recording instances.

    Represents a PAINT project that contains experiments, configuration objects, and references to relevant directories.

    Represents metadata and associated analysis data for a specific recording within an experiment.

    Represents a rectangular region (square) within a recording or experiment, with its coordinates, statistics, and related tracks.
    Track
    The Track class represents the properties and attributes of a trajectory or path recorded during an experiment.
